highlights.text: Ozuna has the most spots on Top Songs Global. “Criminal” is the highest at #21.
“MIC Drop (feat. Desiigner) [Steve Aoki Remix]” by BTS, Desiigner, and Steve Aoki is the highest new entry on Top Songs Global at #71.
“Say You Won't Let Go” by James Arthur has been on Top Songs Global the longest, at 49 weeks straight.
“Last Christmas” by Wham! is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Global, up 95 spots at #60.
